text: Nils Hülphers, sometimes transcribed Hylphert (1712—1776), was a Swedish mayor of Hedemora (1760), and member of the Riksdag of Sweden (1755—1756, 1765—1770). Nils Hülphers was the grandson of :sv:Nils Rabenius and cousin of Abraham Hülphers the Older. ==References== Category:Members of the Riksdag of the Estates Category:Mayors of places in Sweden Category:1712 births Category:1776 deaths Category:People from Hedemora Category:18th-century Swedish politicians
